title: After Mom-of-5 disappears from wealthy enclave, Hubby rips back seats from truck!  WHERE'S JENNIFER DULOS?
itunes:title: After Mom-of-5 disappears from wealthy enclave, Hubby rips back seats from truck!  WHERE'S JENNIFER DULOS?
description:
The estranged husband of missing mother of five, Jennifer Dulos, arrested again on tampering charges. But could those charges lead to a murder charge? Police say her ex-husband and his new girlfriend are prime suspects. Joining Nancy Grace today:

Joseph Scott Morgan: Forensics expert

Dr. Patricia Saunders:  Clinical Psychologist

Alexis Tereszcuk: Radar Online reporter

David Mack:    Syndicated Radio Host
